27
00:02:51,660 --> 00:02:53,155
<b>Thank you so much.</b>

28
00:02:54,190 --> 00:02:55,355
<b>For that.</b>

29
00:02:57,960 --> 00:03:00,265
<b>I have something I want to tell you too.</b>

30
00:03:01,929 --> 00:03:03,435
<b>To me,</b>

31
00:03:05,500 --> 00:03:07,335
<b>you are more valuable</b>

32
00:03:12,540 --> 00:03:14,075
<b>than the name "Bella".</b>

33
00:03:42,610 --> 00:03:43,875
<b>I beg of you.</b>

34
00:03:49,950 --> 00:03:51,445
<b>Please let me do this.</b>

35
00:04:35,730 --> 00:04:38,755
<b>Hello everyone,
it is time for DBC News Interviews.</b>

36
