39
00:04:48,840 --> 00:04:51,008
<b>Yesterday's star was Louis Bellemont,</b>

40
00:04:51,009 --> 00:04:53,505
<b>and today's star is this person.</b>

41
00:04:55,080 --> 00:04:57,849
