61
00:05:55,070 --> 00:05:56,165
<b>I see.</b>

62
00:05:56,270 --> 00:06:00,675
<b>However,
it must not have been an easy decision.</b>

63
00:06:04,250 --> 00:06:07,915
<b>I am the one who made
the real Bella outfit</b>

64
00:06:09,290 --> 00:06:11,515
<b>that was chosen at the opening</b>

65
00:06:12,060 --> 00:06:13,625
<b>of the Bella Boutique yesterday.</b>

66
00:06:14,130 --> 00:06:15,289
<b>Good job!</b>

67
00:06:15,290 --> 00:06:16,555
<b>- Let's go, Bella!
- Way to go!</b>

68
00:06:16,560 --> 00:06:18,329
<b>- Good job!
- Way to go, Bella!</b>

69
00:06:18,330 --> 00:06:20,565
<b>Good job!</b>

70
00:06:20,830 --> 00:06:23,199
<b>She said she made it, so it's over.</b>

71
00:06:23,200 --> 00:06:25,139
<b>- That's right.
[ - Are you happy? ]</b>

72
00:06:25,140 --> 00:06:26,695
