206
00:15:13,730 --> 00:15:15,225
<b>How could you?</b>

207
00:15:57,680 --> 00:16:00,805
<b>[ I just want to make sure
of one tiny detail. ]</b>

208
00:16:01,410 --> 00:16:04,445
<b>I understand you'll be leaving
