209
00:16:04,820 --> 00:16:05,819
<b>Excuse me?</b>

210
00:16:05,820 --> 00:16:09,145
<b>We can't have two Bellas under one sky.</b>

211
00:16:16,060 --> 00:16:17,755
<b>I'm sorry,</b>

212
00:16:17,830 --> 00:16:19,525
<b>but that's none of your business.</b>

213
00:16:23,600 --> 00:16:25,835
<b>You really don't listen.</b>

214
00:16:28,210 --> 00:16:31,175
<b>Chef Moon must go through so much.</b>

215
00:16:35,480 --> 00:16:38,675
<b>I'm saying many unfortunate events
