217
00:16:43,190 --> 00:16:45,615
<b>I didn't expect you to be</b>

218
00:16:45,960 --> 00:16:47,625
<b>this devious.</b>

219
00:16:55,070 --> 00:16:57,765
<b>I guess you overestimated me.</b>

220
00:16:59,670 --> 00:17:02,465
