222
00:17:06,640 --> 00:17:09,375
<b>to achieve what I want.</b>

223
00:17:38,179 --> 00:17:40,945
<b>Yu-jin, do you need me at the lobby now?</b>

224
00:17:45,780 --> 00:17:48,045
<b>Don't look for me.</b>

225
00:17:49,520 --> 00:17:51,455
<b>[ Just forget about me. ]</b>

226
00:17:53,460 --> 00:17:54,985
<b>[ Live a happy life. ]</b>

227
00:17:57,700 --> 00:17:58,955
<b>Where are you now?</b>

228
00:18:01,130 --> 00:18:02,725
<b>I'm going to go somewhere far away.</b>

229
00:18:04,840 --> 00:18:06,739
<b>[ It's now hard for me
to stay in this country, ]</b>

230
00:18:06,740 --> 00:18:08,665
<b>[ and I don't want to anymore. ]</b>

231
00:18:10,170 --> 00:18:12,005
<b>[ I don't think I can handle ]</b>

232
00:18:13,280 --> 00:18:14,975
